he-in...\n\n🎁 PROJECTORS: Get your free guide to the 3 blind spots blocking invitations right now:\n👉 https://www.abigailrebecca.com/free-gift\n\n🔮 Order the Human Design Visibility Guide and align your business strategy to your chart:\n👉 https://www.abigailrebecca.com/visibi...\n\n📸 Follow along on Instagram for more updates and resources:\n👉   / the_visibility_goddess  \n\n#ProjectorBusinessTips #HumanDesignProjector #ProjectorStrategy #WaitingForTheInvitation #AbigailRebecca #HumanDesignForBusiness #AuthenticLeadership #ICONICLeadership #OrchestrateTheInvitation #ProjectorSuccess","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":834,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJoCEM2rARgBIhMI4Pq_r-LZkwMVF0Q4BR2AFjQTSPCP5Ki0x9vY0AHKAQRIyZNc","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTM0X0NJVnE4MHp0akJXbXp4ZG93bFoyLXdzd3xBQ3Jtc0tsSmJWVE1zRlNQLWF1QTdqM01ZTFdlY3h2ZHp4ZGl2djZJZlktM2d2RHAwemJPRl9FU1ZTSzR1cFdQRDF6ckk1RU5lXzZUUzdhOEttSDdLZUY5YkRtUmZEY2tOT2FpNVlRN0c5RU9fTktVMXVxOTB3dw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abigailrebecca.com%2Fthe-invitation\u0026v=0LFuO0UZB_A","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTM0X0NJVnE4MHp0akJXbXp4ZG93bFoyLXdzd3xBQ3Jtc0tsSmJWVE1zRlNQLWF1QTdqM01ZTFdlY3h2ZHp4ZGl2djZJZlktM2d2RHAwemJPRl9FU1ZTSzR1cFdQRDF6ckk1RU5lXzZUUzdhOEttSDdLZUY5YkRtUmZEY2tOT2FpNVlRN0c5RU9fTktVMXVxOTB3dw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abigailrebecca.com%2Fthe-invitation\u0026v=0LFuO0UZB_A","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":967,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJoCEM2rARgBIhMI4Pq_r-LZkwMVF0Q4BR2AFjQTSPCP5Ki0x9vY0AHKAQRIyZNc","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXNPLXNFNHBxUTNIci0yc0ljLXBGS0x1T0NFUXxBQ3Jtc0trNF9FTEt2NHF1a01hNHJEU3